I was lucky enough to win an Initial Evaluation, which was donated by Your Dog Guru, at a charity auction.
From the start, I have been impressed with the quality of service I received.
Jimi was prompt and clear in his communication, as well as accommodating to my schedule.
He was calm and respectful while working with my dogs (a Boxer and Miniature Dachshund) and, without much information from me, accurately assessed their issues--exactly as I experience them.
He asked appropriate questions and gave me plenty of time to ask mine.
He provided practical guidance and since I have implemented some of his suggestions, my experience with my dogs has improved.
Observing him work with the dog that accompanied him was inspiring!
Jimi is fun to work with and above all, conducts himself and his business with integrity.

