I rescued Maggie from a very neglectful situation and when I got her home I didn't realize the amount of trauma she had.
She was anxious and afraid of everything and everyone.
I didn't think she would ever be "normal".
Jimi not only helped me with her commands but he also fixed her fear issues.
Thank you for everything!!

